Titolo: Midwinter (video game)

Anno: 1989

Descrizione: Midwinter is a post-apocalyptic first-person action role-playing game with strategy and survival elements for the Atari ST, Amiga and PC. It was designed by Mike Singleton and released in 1989 by Microplay Software. The game was critically acclaimed and commercially successful enough to get a sequel titled Flames of Freedom in 1991.

Genere: Action role-playing game

Valutazione: N/A
